! Fractal Extendable Hair Field

A nested active fibril surface that changes extension, stiffness, tip mode,
and orientation for contact.

!! Why It Matters

It makes locally adaptive material contact concrete enough to score: extension
depth, attachment mode, failure limits, and response latency.

